  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever is going to happen, but we would like you and my oldest brother was that time with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they were talking with some Gentiles that they lived, you know, like, next door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they liked us, and they didn't see-- they didn't want to see us, you know, being killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he was afraid to, to make some arrangements for us, because it was next door, and, and it was suspicious.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If it would have been suspicious, you know, he was afraid that they might come and look.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he made arrangements with another, with a brother-in-law, friend, I think, which lived a little bit away, a couple of blocks away from us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a few weeks before we knew that we have to leave-- that the ghetto-- that we have to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they, they went, they had-- it was a small house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a barn next to this house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And under this barn, they dug out a, a bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how you would call it here-- an, an area maybe?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe it's 8 by 10, 6 by-- I don't know, something, underneath this barn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and we were supposed to go in there and stay there, because we didn't-- I mean, everybody thought, maybe it's not going to last.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody-- every time some, some news came, that the Russians are getting stronger, and this and that, and maybe they'll pull back.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
